white swimsuit, island energy, ocean muse, sunkissed skin, main character, glow state
#modelmuse #islandgirl #travelwithme #vacationfashion #waterbaby #tannedskin

Have you ever walked barefoot on grass in a flowy dress? That’s my definition of everything we forget to value.

We chase the loud things –the sleek car, the perfect apartment, the designer wardrobe. And don’t get me wrong, I love a good outfit. But lately I’ve realized that the tiniest, quietest moments– the warm sun, soft grass, and the feeling of your dress catching the breeze brings a different kind of happiness.

The kind that doesn’t scream.
It just settles into your bones.
That’s the kind of soft luxury I’m after these days.
